{"tid":526122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[相由心生] IU慶功宴與路人親切合影 大方把別桌的賬也結了","createTime":"2018-01-11T10:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T15:38:19.000Z","uid":34643,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22cde70ea0ede2cadc3e6cc34a2977ea1e3e2b05","tid":526122,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTOQrzNWAAIO6Xl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTOQrzNWAAIO6Xl.jpg&h=c572657c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTOQrzQW0AArrTq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTOQrzQW0AArrTq.jpg&h=a9f66e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼心合影<br />\n<br />\n網易娛樂1月11日報道 據台灣媒體報道，韓國金唱片頒獎禮於10、11日舉行，歌手IU不僅獲得了Digital音源本賞，更獲得了音源大賞，她在致詞中感謝了所有工作人員，也俏皮地說&ldquo;待會去吃慶功宴吧！&rdquo;她不僅在慶功宴親切和路人合照，更直接大方請在場所有客人吃飯，消息一傳出讓網友直呼&ldquo;超羨慕&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIU在10日的金唱片頒獎典禮中，分別獲得Digital音源本賞和音源大賞，她開心地在台上感謝所有喜歡《夜信》的人，也將這份榮耀與作曲、編曲家共享，&ldquo;再次感謝IU TEAM，現在應該比我還要開心吧，待會去慶功宴吧！&rdquo;在典禮結束後，他們也到首爾某烤肉店慶功，原本就在裡面的客人看到IU很是驚喜，上前請求合照也獲得同意。<br />\n<br />\n光是和IU合照就已經夠讓網友羨慕了，結果11日出現一篇題為&ldquo;聽說IU請吃肉了！&rdquo;的文章，仔細一看內容得知，&ldquo;認識的妹妹和朋友在烤肉店吃飯，結果發現隔壁桌是IU！那間店原本有3桌客人，IU得了大賞在慶祝，連在場客人的帳單也一起付了，太羨慕了！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTMfaZkUQAAVQv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTMfaZkUQAAVQv4.jpg&h=15ec6f48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40af149c63cc4306d9af6249ac0ec63452ba95ec","tid":526122,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"中產u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdb2387c20c062c6b55760bcf71a0c7b883ecb6","tid":526122,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"IU好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d7ab98112ac95397eb98903f4312e0276b91c9","tid":526122,"uid":34498,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"IU真係呢個世界上最完美嘅女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8768ca8ead4eea0bfe4d353ff11f7e03a216e24d","tid":526122,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d7ab98112ac95397eb98903f4312e0276b91c9","tid":526122,"uid":34498,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"IU真係呢個世界上最完美嘅女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd59c9f20c3834e2e27e54fd20fe0dcca82c61d5","tid":526122,"uid":34686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"屌好想住韓國,出街都可以比IU請食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b53133a659abbb18647587ad88938120d5cc02f","tid":526122,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd59c9f20c3834e2e27e54fd20fe0dcca82c61d5","tid":526122,"uid":34686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"屌好想住韓國,出街都可以比IU請食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"重可以面貼面合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65c7f60de5640c9ae35728960df75ceefeab224","tid":526122,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"等睇有人話公關做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d12a95fafcd65d85ee2f59cf79349db9cd9f87f","tid":526122,"uid":34643,"lik